normalised: Tumchim toksim ghevnk zai! Udharonnak, M-M-R toksim Measles, Mumps ani Rubella virudd rakxon korot. Toxi vellapatrakhatir vo toksim ghevnuk axil'lea uprant ekxim degree Fahrenheit-antli tap ail'leantar tor tumchea Doctoracho sol'lo gheiat.
